{
  "stem": "16473.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 459.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I went because I had to.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But after that, we didn't go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So she knew that that was really dangerous.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then nobody ventured out of the basement, which is called the bunker.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then after a while, after we had been there a while, a woman crawled over, over the shooting.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I forgot to mention, we-- this building was next to a railroad embankment so it provided a natural cover.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the shooting was going on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "First, the Russians were-- or the Nazis were-- later on, Nazis were shooting at the Russians.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Then the Russians used our building, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Nazis used our building, Russians used our building-- because of that embankment where they could shoot over that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And so this woman crawled over through the crossfire of bullets.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And she begged for food because her daughter had been shot in the breast.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They had no food.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And all the people who lived there collectively said that no, they couldn't spare any food.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "There was no food to spare.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And my mother said, I'm going to give her my food, you cannot do this.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And indeed, what she did is she gave her portion, probably for that day.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Because by then there was no individual food, it wasn't mine or yours.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Except these girls were given rations by their mother, which I envied so much.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They had goose fat.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And goose, you know, the fat keeps the goose fresh.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And they got to go into that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And mother never let me have any of it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And that was never declared as common stock.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And everybody had their own little thing which they would not put into common stock.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But for the most part, everything was common, and so it was a collective decision.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
